730
00:41:34,292 --> 00:41:35,727
Governor!

731
00:41:35,761 --> 00:41:37,596
We're in! We're in!

732
00:41:37,629 --> 00:41:39,030
We're in, governor!

733
00:41:39,064 --> 00:41:42,734
You've been nominated
on the 46th ballot!

734
00:41:42,768 --> 00:41:44,570
Oh, papa! Oh, daddy!

735
00:41:44,603 --> 00:41:45,637
Congratulations,
governor.

736
00:41:45,671 --> 00:41:47,739
Ha ha ha!
Ha ha ha!

737
