Oh.
It couldn't be.

1806
01:52:02,116 --> 01:52:03,450
I'm sure of it.

1807
01:52:03,484 --> 01:52:05,419
Ah, don't kid me.

1808
01:52:05,452 --> 01:52:08,022
Why don't you
go and ask her?

1809
